					<p>Find me all over the web (mostly)!</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="/ideas/" class=" [ gamma ] "><c-emoji>💡</c-emoji>/ideas</a>
					<p>Things I’d like to work on.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="/interests/" class=" [ gamma ] "><c-emoji>⭐</c-emoji>/interests</a>
