				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="/podroll/" class=" [ gamma ] "><c-emoji>🎙️</c-emoji>/podroll</a>
					<p>A list of podcasts that I enjoy.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="/sitemap/" class=" [ gamma ] "><c-emoji>🗺️</c-emoji>/sitemap</a>
					<p><em>All</em> the pages on this website.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="/uses/" class=" [ gamma ] "><c-emoji>🛠️</c-emoji>/uses</a>
