					<p>Your right to privacy on this website.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="/88x31/" class=" [ gamma ] "><c-emoji>🖌️</c-emoji>88x31</a>
					<p>A list of 88x31 badges I’ve made.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="/ghoti/" class=" [ gamma ] "><c-emoji>🤷</c-emoji>The Absurdity of English</a>
